    "created": "2026-02-10T15:45:25.463002",
    "datastore_active": false,
    "description": "This dataset provides a reference mapping between substation numbers and substation names used within the LTDS CIM Power System Model. It is intended to support users who need to join or link the LTDS CIM model with other datasets available on the portal. For example: combining network topology with asset, geospatial, or operational datasets that reference substations by ID or name. \r\n\r\nThe dataset contains:\r\n\r\n* Substation Number \u2013 the unique identifier often used for substations\r\n* Substation Type \u2013 Grid Supply Point, Bulk Supply Point, etc.\r\n* Substation Name \u2013 the substation name in the LTDS CIM Power System Model\r\n\r\nBy offering a clean lookup between these identifiers, the dataset simplifies cross dataset integration and ensures consistency when analysing or enriching LTDS CIM network data. ",
